</a>
</h4></div><div><div class="blog-summary">In the summer of 2022 I (James Fawcett) walked from Denver to Durango on the Colorado Trail. I started the walk alone and eighteen years old, having…
</div></div><span class="views-field views-field-field-date"><span class="field-content date-display-single">August 21, 2024
</span></span>|<span><span class="field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/james-fawcett" hreflang="en">James Fawcett</a>, <a href="/author/madeline-meyers" hreflang="en">Madeline Meyers</a>
</span></span></div>
<div class="views-row"><div class="views-field views-field-field-blog-category"><div class="field-content field-name-field-blog-category"><a href="/blog-categories/interviews" hreflang="en">Interviews</a>
</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-thumbnail"><div class="field-content imageleft"> <a href="/blog/interviews/more-one-life-conversation-lyn-coffin-alaaeldin-mahmoud" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/blog_thumbnail/public/CoffinAnchor-w.jpg?itok=keCluKS6" width="100" height="75" alt="A photograph of Lyn Coffin at a poetry conference" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-blog-thumbnail" />
